    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid, reliable shape and has been well-cared for over the years. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways, it runs like a dream and is totally ready for its next chapter with a new owner. I'd love for you to come by, take a look, and see how great it feels behind the wheel!",
      "price": 32500.0,
