      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pure mechanical experience, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox, delivering torque through a factory M Variable Differential Lock. Technical highlights include a documented VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to maintain chassis integrity. The suspension geometry remains true, offering the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance these chassis are renowned for. While the exterior reflects its history as a driver's car, the mechanical vitals are robust, featuring consistent compression across all cylinders and a sharp, responsive throttle map. It is an ideal specimen for the enthusiast who prioritizes drivetrain performance and structural soundness.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
