      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m selling my car and it\u2019s honestly been such a treat to own. It\u2019s in really solid condition, runs beautifully, and has been kept nice and tidy. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve loved driving this beauty, and I know you will too! Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
